# CI/CD Pipeline Security Diagram

direction: right

developer: Developer
git_repo: Git Repository
ci_server: CI Server
scan_stage: Security Scan
build_stage: Build Container
test_stage: Test Stage
sign_stage: Sign Image
registry: Container Registry
deploy_stage: Deploy
production: Production

developer --> git_repo: Push Code
git_repo --> ci_server: Trigger Pipeline
ci_server --> scan_stage: Code Scan
scan_stage --> build_stage: Build
build_stage --> test_stage: Test
test_stage --> sign_stage: Sign
sign_stage --> registry: Push Image
registry --> deploy_stage: Deploy
deploy_stage --> production: Release
